{"tid":1655452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港抗爭延燒 網傳中共2支人馬「地下執法」 包括暗殺、滅口","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T13:14:59.000Z","uid":35790,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cd600b47c2a3d53d7c3536728362ae9b45d85544","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭延燒 網傳中共2支人馬「地下執法」 包括暗殺、滅口<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-15<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕香港反送中持續4個月，港警暴力鎮壓不斷升級，並爆出多起多起年輕人失蹤、自殺及被殺案，引發香港社會人心惶惶，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而根據網友的最新爆料，指逾2萬名來自中共的公安、武警及秘密特工，已經進入香港進行「地下執法」，當中分成2股力量，一是冒充港警執行捉捕及清場；另一支來自中共國安人員組成的「祕密特工」，執行竊聽、綁架及謀殺棄屍等。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n這起訊息來自署名「君子蘭」的網友在推特上爆料，他連發數文詳述暗殺力量的存在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據君子蘭的說法，這兩支暗藏在港警之中的力量，一支是中共廣東公安和武警，直接穿上加入港警制服，跟港警一起動作，負責在示威現場驅散、毆打、捉捕、清場任務；不同的是，這群冒充港警的公安已獲得高層授意，可以「在捉捕示威者過程中會肆無忌憚地過分使用武力」，且不會承擔任何的法律後果。<br />\n<br />\n另一支地下執法的力量，來自中共國安所屬的秘密特工，直接聽命北京國安部和廣東國安廳指揮，且可以指揮港警，除了少數合作對象外，不會在港警系統上留下任何紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n這隊人馬主要負責對示威運動的核心人物進行電訊竊聽、跟蹤偵查、綁架密捕、刑訊迫供、謀殺棄屍的祕密任務，目的是要查清示威活動的核心人物、示威者間的互動方式、領導機構&hellip;&hellip;..等內容，以打擊瓦解示威運動。<br />\n<br />\n為達目的，這支祕密特工甚至不惜使用包括恐嚇引誘、暴力折磨、強姦輪姦、催眠餵藥，對不合作者一概會被自殺、棄屍。<br />\n<br />\n君子蘭更說，即使目前香港已經出現多起無名屍，未來可能還會有更多人「被自殺」及發現更多無名屍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2946314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2946314&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9EcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=4a1e2eb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/world/breakingnews/2946314</a>"},{"pid":"04d68d56cfbb5bd2ad4b0e1412a568f10cf66fe5","tid":1655452,"uid":289978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"係咪即係世界各國有藉口出兵支共?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbec678ec68d20869e3f45bd727857808fd782dc","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://twitter.com/newyorkluo/status/1183531693396971520/photo/1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewyorkluo%2Fstatus%2F1183531693396971520%2Fphoto%2F1&h=198b25ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cf0f15c366283ece711ef3f8428bbffc5c95ece","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/newyorkluo/status/1183531693396971520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fnewyorkluo%2Fstatus%2F1183531693396971520&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9EcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=0b051596\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/newyorkluo/status/1183531693396971520</a>"},{"pid":"3806f0a73dd9c3a8fa6e63faebe1f6001207091d","tid":1655452,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04d68d56cfbb5bd2ad4b0e1412a568f10cf66fe5","tid":1655452,"uid":289978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"係咪即係世界各國有藉口出兵支共?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"首先要搵到證據"},{"pid":"fb3aaeff25fd944928400a06e16c7823b06c7273","tid":1655452,"uid":41963,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"成日傳<br />\n垃圾共產黨永遠都係有虛冇實"},{"pid":"f7695fa34f7de21f0fa85c02cf670ca2d767faa2","tid":1655452,"uid":34336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b11528ff809880fd29bd97c5ae67959fc76c5ca8","tid":1655452,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3806f0a73dd9c3a8fa6e63faebe1f6001207091d","tid":1655452,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04d68d56cfbb5bd2ad4b0e1412a568f10cf66fe5","tid":1655452,"uid":289978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"係咪即係世界各國有藉口出兵支共?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:32:06.000Z","msg":"首先要搵到證據"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"呢篇野已經可以係証據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為各國一早想出兵支共好耐<br />\n只係差個藉口"},{"pid":"f4051aa6ebe89a08b886ba6adb43fd7ef108bd53","tid":1655452,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓<br />\n今日起到區議會選舉前<br />\n每人感化一個藍絲變黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要真．文宣!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654696</a>"},{"pid":"7e764be82e6d64f68d4de4ac967ad217bf3388fb","tid":1655452,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7MNgLMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7MNgLMr.png&h=f90ad1a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNKGcrs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNKGcrs.png&h=351b8c75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9349ca352c82f20c59e4f19aba629c48379d62a2","tid":1655452,"uid":36287,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"所以堆弱智仲信有大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c41f85b0bf301037e0bc112fcc6948b7eb452f","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e639dece7a2f701b975c4e5e71e3fd786f37af46","tid":1655452,"uid":271750,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:46:41.000Z","msg":"唔係好認同。<br />\n其實對付無大台嘅運動，政府以暗殺去達到&quot;止暴&quot;嘅作用根本行唔通。<br />\n風險亦好大。"},{"pid":"faf44d1cff27b971f7041bd85fe0eea678d692b0","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1c5d3ca1a99851d8052092855cc7d83d8c1a8a8c","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d9d179b1bb7f87ad4f3d32d5f7e7faa3013490e8","tid":1655452,"uid":293227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"幾十個手足一早比人殺左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789b1479c25b0ef85acc9987bbb66daf6e586da0","tid":1655452,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"港警露「北方口音」：趕緊走了嘿（視頻）<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-15<br />\n<br />\n港警露「北方口音」：趕緊走了嘿（視頻）<br />\n<br />\n一些港警對待示威民眾的殘忍手段與中共軍警更如出一轍，令民眾懷疑中共軍警或已混入港警隊伍，執行暴力鎮壓的命令。（Anthony Kwan/Getty Images）<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2019年10月15日訊】日前推特上熱傳一段視頻，在畫面中可見有港警疑似露出「北方口音」，對其他港警高喊「趕緊走了嘿」、「走了，走了，趕緊的」。視頻引發網友熱議，紛紛指真的是「大陸公安來了」。<br />\n<br />\n「十一」過後，香港警方的暴力鎮壓不降反升，一些港警對待示威民眾的殘忍手段與中共軍警更如出一轍，令民眾懷疑中共軍警或已混入港警隊伍，執行暴力鎮壓的命令。<br />\n<br />\n10月9日，有網友在海外社交媒體推特上發布一段視頻，視頻中顯示疑似「速龍小隊」在撤退時，其中一人「疑似帶有北方口音」，他對著後方其他人用普通話大喊「趕緊走了嘿！」<br />\n<br />\n隨後又有一個較粗的男聲用普通話叫道「走了走了，趕緊的！」在他們大聲喊話時，現場拍攝的兩名記者就站在旁邊。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，有三名落後的「速龍小隊成員」陸續出現在鏡頭前，他們一個個舉槍朝人群方向密集開槍，疑似發射橡膠子彈和胡椒彈。<br />\n<br />\n該網友在貼文中怒斥：在中共邪黨的善惡顛倒的獎懲制度下，這些家伙越發的沒人性了。看他們面對人群開槍有多隨意，就知他們有多冷酷。<br />\n<br />\n清楚的北方口音❗️可以確定這些傢伙來自大陸‼️<br />\n<br />\n「趕緊走了嘿！」<br />\n<br />\n「走了，走了，趕緊的！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/cindywei2017/status/1182270962689032192?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1182270962689032192&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2Fa102686207.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fcindywei2017%2Fstatus%2F1182270962689032192%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1182270962689032192%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ntdtv.com%252Fb5%252F2019%252F10%252F15%252Fa102686207.html&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9EcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=f5e8d206\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/cindywei2017/status/1182270962689032192?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1182270962689032192&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2Fa102686207.html</a><br />\n🔹在中共邪黨的善惡顛倒的獎懲制度下，這些傢伙越發的沒人性了。看他們面對人群開槍有多隨意，就知他們有多冷酷。<br />\n<br />\n下午8:25 - 2019年10月10日<br />\n<br />\n這段視頻曝光後引起網友熱議，有大陸網友留言指出，「確實是大陸公安來了」又指「即使是大陸公安都很正常啊」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社近日引述外交界消息指，自香港反送中以來，中共駐港部門人數至少增加了一倍，9月底的所謂「換防」就是變相增兵，進駐香港的還包括大量中共武警。<br />\n<br />\n近日有香港警察在網上爆料指，每次有大型示威活動，自己和一些同事就「被放假」，並要上交肩章、警號。<br />\n<br />\n這名警察還說，他看到自己警區的警察蒙面執勤回來，就上去打招呼，對方卻不理睬他。而且有同事聽到，一些「速龍小隊成員」在衛生間講普通話。他們懷疑自己的身份被混入香港警隊的中共軍警盜用。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動持續4個多月來，港警對示威者的暴力鎮壓越來越血腥殘酷，「港警」打斷男示威者四肢甚至頸椎，性侵女示威者，製造8.31太子站慘案和密集的「被自殺」事件，均被懷疑是中共軍警特務的「專業手法」。<br />\n<br />\n10月14日，署名「君子蘭」的網友在推特上爆料，指逾2萬名來自中共的公安、武警及秘密特工，已經進入香港進行「地下執法」，當中分成2股力量，一是冒充港警執行抓捕及清場；另一支來自中共國安人員組成的「祕密特工」，執行竊聽、綁架及謀殺棄屍等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/10/15/a102686207.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2019%2F10%2F15%2Fa102686207.html&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9EcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=88a8862f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.ntdtv.com/b5/2019/10/15/a102686207.html</a>"},{"pid":"0e38cb04a97b76119b7307f3ca24f5aeec1f90e8","tid":1655452,"uid":105924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e639dece7a2f701b975c4e5e71e3fd786f37af46","tid":1655452,"uid